{"id": "24945", "post": "<div class=\"post-24945 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-ddos tag-poll tag-poll-results\" id=\"post-24945\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/poll-results-have-you-been-the-victim-of-a-ddos-attack/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Poll Results: Have You Been the Victim of a DDoS Attack?</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/ddos/\" rel=\"tag\">ddos</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/poll/\" rel=\"tag\">poll</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/poll-results/\" rel=\"tag\">poll results</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODdhAQABAPAAAMPDwwAAACwAAAAAAQABAAACAkQBADs=\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \"> October 5, 2020 @ 12:00 pm, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI0MTYiIGhlaWdodD0iMjQ1IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNDE2IDI0NSI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/lowendbox-poll-results.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"416\" height=\"245\"></a></p><p>Back on September 22, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/poll-have-you-been-the-victim-of-a-ddos-attack/\">we asked you</a> if you had ever been the victim of a DDoS attack.&nbsp; These sorts of attacks are continuing to increase \u2013 by <a href=\"https://betanews.com/2020/09/21/500-percent-ddos-increase/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">one report</a>, by over 500% over the last year.</p><p>57% of those responding to our poll said that they had been victimized by this type of attack.&nbsp; This is not surprising since LEB/LET readers are often using their VPSes for game servers (a huge magnet) and public-facing web services.</p><p>Of those who were attacked, about have said service was quickly restored or impact was minimal.&nbsp; But for those who were significantly impacted,&nbsp;53% of those had their service offline for a significant period of time.&nbsp; 20% had to purchase DDoS mitigation.&nbsp; One in six respondents had their service terminated or had to change series, and one in twelve lost money because of the business impact.&nbsp; 3% had to pay network overage fees.</p><p>About 40% of respondents said their provider\u2019s DDoS mitigation service stopped the attack, while another 23% used a third party (e.g., CloudFlare).&nbsp; But nearly 1 in 6 had to move to a new provider.</p><p>Thanks everyone for participating!</p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2NjQiIGhlaWdodD0iMjUwIiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjY0IDI1MCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone  wp-image-24946\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos1.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"664\" height=\"250\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos1.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos1-300x113.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos1-768x289.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 664px) 100vw, 664px\"></p><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI2OTAiIGhlaWdodD0iNTE2IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNjkwIDUxNiI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone  wp-image-24947\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos2.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"690\" height=\"516\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos2.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos2-300x224.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos2-768x574.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\"> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI3NDAiIGhlaWdodD0iNTE0IiB2aWV3Qm94PSIwIDAgNzQwIDUxNCI+PHJlY3Qgd2lkdGg9IjEwMCUiIGhlaWdodD0iMTAwJSIgZmlsbD0iI2NmZDRkYiIvPjwvc3ZnPg==\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone  wp-image-24948\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos3.png.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"740\" height=\"514\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos3.png.webp 800w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos3-300x209.png.webp 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/poll_ddos3-768x534.png.webp 768w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fpoll-results-have-you-been-the-victim-of-a-ddos-attack%2F&amp;t=Poll%20Results%3A%20Have%20You%20Been%20the%20Victim%20of%20a%20DDoS%20Attack%3F\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow